You can refine the descriptors for your sport, but the key is **consistency**: athletes must understand what ‚Äú5‚Äù vs ‚Äú8‚Äù feels like in the context of your training.

**Coach Takeaway:**\
**RPE is the athlete‚Äôs internal ‚Äúvolume knob‚Äù for effort.** When used consistently, it becomes a simple language you and your players share about session intensity.

